  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    VAT for businesses if there's no Brexit deal
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    How VAT rules for UK businesses trading with EU countries would be affected if the UK leaves the EU without a deal. 
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

